{"tid":1091487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻省理工學院終止與華為、中興合作夥伴關係","createTime":"2019-04-04T07:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T07:20:13.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c47aa60411e589b3cb859e7952437128740bbbb4","tid":1091487,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:17:39.000Z","msg":"世界一流大學之一、美國麻省理工學院（MIT）終止與華為和中興等中國電信製造商的合作關係，並加強對來自中國等國家的合作提議的審核程序。<br />\n<br />\n麻省理工學院主管科研的副校長祖博爾在一份聲明中說：「由於美國聯邦政府有關違反制裁法的調查，麻省理工學院不再接受來自華為和中興及其子公司的新項目或續延正在進行的項目。」<br />\n<br />\n美國政府指稱華為公司盜竊美國技術和違反美國對伊朗的制裁法之後，美國、英國和澳大利亞的幾家一流大學、包括斯坦福大學和牛津大學，宣佈停止接受來自華為公司的資金。<br />\n<br />\n麻省理工學院的聲明說，對有些國家的項目，除進行所有國際項目都必須接受的審核之外，還要進行額外的學術及行政審核，這些國家有含香港的中國、俄羅斯以及沙特阿拉伯，審查的重點風險包括知識產權、出口管制、政治權利、公民權、人權以及是否符合麻省理工學院的核心價值觀和學術使命。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/mit-cuts-collaborations-with-huawei-zte/4861401.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fmit-cuts-collaborations-with-huawei-zte%2F4861401.html&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvNjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=6fadd119\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/mit-cuts-collaborations-with-huawei-zte/4861401.html</a>"},{"pid":"88f7d558e258e0b3174f3c1ac4445980e25f695f","tid":1091487,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">LATE BETTER THAN NEVER！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"61548a99f98da8bd27d979c6820629fbed4324f3","tid":1091487,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"最高學府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cd0c1a47603afe3ef3696b0f198b59e36f68e3","tid":1091487,"uid":17765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"可以自煮燃發 <br />\n支匪又贏"}]}